                            <p class="fw-bold text-success mb-2">Why use this site?</p>
                            <h3 class="fw-bold">First off - HOW did you use this site? It's hosted locally. Please
                                reach
                                out.
                            </h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="py-5 p-lg-5">
                        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 mx-auto" style="max-width: 900px;">
                            <div class="col mb-5">
                                <div class="card shadow-sm">
                                    <div class="card-body px-4 py-5 px-md-5">
                                        <div class="bs-icon-lg d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-3 bs-icon"
                                            style="top: 1rem;right: 1rem;position: absolute;">
